本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:莊偉聖研究生(外文):Wei-Sheng Chuang論文名稱:臨終者追求生命意義與價值之生命教育啟示－以三部電影文本為例論文名稱(外文):The Enlightening of Life Education from the Dying Who Pursue the Meanings and Values of Life － Examples from Three Movies指導教授:鈕則誠指導教授(外文):niu tse-cheng學位類別:碩士校院名稱:銘傳大學系所名稱:教育研究所碩士班學門:教育學門學類:綜合教育學類論文出版年:2010畢業學年度:98語文別:中文論文頁數:173中文關鍵詞:臨終、生命價值、生命意義、生命教育、電影外文關鍵詞:life education、dying、film、movie、value of life、mean of life、end-of-life相關次數:

被引用:9點閱:1436評分:下載:509書目收藏:7



此篇論文由〈普通高級中學課程綱要〉生命教育中的三門課題「生命與科技倫理、生死關懷、人格統整與靈性發展」為骨架，分析並闡釋三部電影《終極假期》、《一路玩到掛》、《生之慾》中的「臨終者」感受，進以挖掘出生命意義與價值的意涵、觀點、方向、及可行途徑，最後給予生命意義與價值上的建議。本研究以〈普通高級中學課程綱要〉之生命教育為「概念文本」，三部電影為「分析文本」，以「文本分析法」的研究方法闡述臨終者對生命意義與價值在生命教育中的啟示，藉由逐字稿、畫面詮釋、電影語言、角色描述、影評、幕後解說等方式分析並闡釋之。從三部電影中歸結出下列結論：一、其「意涵與觀點」為下列所述：（一）主角對生命意義的具體覺察在於醫師。（二）「家屬、愛人」與「臨終者」之間的關係對生命意義與價值有其影響。（三）生命意義在於工作職責、情感體驗、苦痛體驗、奉獻自我；生命價值在於充實感、完滿感、體現自我、省思自我等知覺感受。二、其「可行途徑」為下列所述：（一）確立自我生命定義（二）批次訂立人生目標：依生命意義擬定最終目標、依各年齡階段訂定目標（三）體現生活與情感：體驗生命－過程的行動、實現生命－目標的達成紀錄、體現情感（四）省思自我生命定義：快樂與否、價值與否（五）回顧生命，健康看待死亡

     This study is composed of “life and ethics of science and technology” “concerned of life and death”, and “Personal integrity and Spiritual development” as a framework from three topics of Life Education in “Senior High schools’ outline of curriculum”.  It not only analyzes the feeling of “the dying” from three movies included “Last Vacation” “The Bucket List”, and “IKIRU” ,but also unearth the meaning of life and value, concepts, aspects, and practicable gateway.  Last but not least, it gives suggestions to the meaning of life and value.     This research was based on the “text of concept” from Life Education in  “Senior High schools’ outline of curriculum” and three movies as a “text of analysis”.  It not only used “Textual Analysis” as the research method to expound the dying’s inspiration on the meaning of life and value but analyze it by many ways, such as verbatim, explanation of frame, film languages, descriptions of characters, film review, backstage narrations, and so on.  We came to conclusions from the three movies:I. Its aspects and concepts are listed below:　a. The main character’s concrete detection about the meaning of life is on the doctor.　b. The relationships among “family members, spouse/lover” and “the dying”have an impact on the meaning of life and value.　c. The meaning of life is to have the responsibilities of jobs, undergo an experience of affections and sufferings, and dedicate ourselves to others; the value of life is to feel our sensations such as fulfillment, satisfaction, self-actualization, and self-reflection, etc..II. Its practicable gateway is listed below:　a. Establish the meaning of life firmly by self.　b. Set up human- life goals: to set up final goals according to the meaning of life and phase of each age.　c. Undergo an experience of life and affections: to experience life---actions of processes, to achieve life---a record of reaching goals, and to experience affections.　d. Reflect the meaning of life: whether happy /valuable or not　e. Retrospect life and see death as healthy

